## Next Steps

To run the full pipeline:

```bash
# 1. Generate full dataset (~20k images)
python dataset/generate_synthetic.py

# 2. Train the model (requires GPU for reasonable speed)
python training/train.py --epochs 10 --batch_size 2

# 3. Run inference
python inference/predict.py --image dataset/images/img_000001.png --model_dir model/brahmi_trocr
```
